title: Legends of the Dark Knight: Superstitious and Cowardly
description:
Done n' done!

I'll say, uploading Legends of The Dark Knight as individual stories was one of the most tedious things i've ever done! I don't even care for a lot of the stories! But hopefully it now be more convinient for others to tell apart the gold from the turds, and not having to download a whole series to find the single Mike Mignola or Eddie Campbell.

This is:

Superstitious and Cowardly (214)
By Christos N. Gage and Phil Winslade
Batman once again finds himself at odds with Deadshot, as the infamous assassin has been contracted to kill an important witness in an upcoming mob trial.
